	"This is an improvement of about 10 seconds over 
	[a href=/1591S 
		"AKA's recently published run
	]a
	" of The Karate Kid. I found a way to do the first screen faster within minutes of fooling around, and since the movie was only in the 3-minute range I went all the way to the end with it.
	$LF
